Steps to upload project on github using git 

1. open project & create .gitigore (to ignore files which not to upload like: node_modules, .env)
2. type command git init 
3. type command git add . ( to add all files )
4. type command git status ( to check current status )
5. type command git commit -m "comments" ( to commit )
git commit -a --allow-empty-message -m " " (without comment)

6. Create repository on github account and copy https links from code section 
7. type git  remote add origing < paset link here >
8. type git remote -v to verify above step
9. type git push origin main

10.type rm -rf .git (to un initialize git) on gitbash
